sources.description:
A group of friends, looking for a place to party, break into an abandoned film studio. Amusing themselves by screening some old movies, they stumble across what appears to be a snuff film featuring a brutal masked murder. They soon begin to suspect they might be the victims in the sequel when they find themselves pursued by the same masked killer.
2025. Stars: Tashi Higgins, Janice Quinol, Samuel Kay
